      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Personal Information:</span> When you sign up
        for Helios Energy, we may collect your name, email address, and other
        necessary information to provide you with our services.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Usage Information:</span> We collect information
