  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-8 p-8 rounded shadow">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Terms of Use</h1>

    <p class="mb-4 italic">
      By using Helios Energy, you agree to the following terms:
